RUNTIME COMPONENT NOTICE (libkrunfw / libkrun)

msbd does NOT bundle or link the microVM runtime. On first run, the
microsandbox SDK's EnsureInstalled downloads the `msb` supervisor and
`libkrunfw` from the upstream microsandbox GitHub release matching the pinned
SDK version, into ~/.microsandbox/ on the host that runs msbd.

libkrunfw and libkrun are licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License
(LGPL). They are obtained, installed, and executed on the end user's host at
runtime — they are not part of, statically linked into, or distributed with the
msbd binary or container image. Operators who choose to redistribute those
downloaded runtime artifacts are responsible for complying with their LGPL
terms.

